original_query: SELECT p.OwnerUserId, v.UserId FROM comments as c, posts as p, postHistory as ph, votes as v, users as u WHERE v.UserId = u.Id AND c.UserId = u.Id AND p.OwnerUserId = u.Id AND ph.UserId = u.Id AND p.ViewCount>=5 AND p.AnswerCount>=0 AND p.AnswerCount<=5 AND ph.PostHistoryTypeId=2 AND ph.CreationDate>=CAST('2010-11-05 01:25:39' AS TIMESTAMP) AND ph.CreationDate<=CAST('2014-09-09 07:14:12' AS TIMESTAMP) AND v.BountyAmount>=0 AND v.BountyAmount<=100 AND v.CreationDate>=CAST('2010-07-26 00:00:00' AS TIMESTAMP) AND u.Views>=0 AND u.Views<=13
rewritten_query: CREATE VIEW E4 AS SELECT votes.userid AS E4_userid FROM votes AS votes WHERE votes.bountyamount >= 0 AND votes.bountyamount <= 100 AND votes.creationdate >= TIMESTAMP '2010-07-26 00:00:00'
CREATE VIEW E2 AS SELECT posts.owneruserid AS E2_owneruserid FROM posts AS posts WHERE posts.viewcount >= 5 AND (posts.answercount >= 0 AND posts.answercount <= 5)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E4_stage1_0 AS SELECT * FROM E4 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E2 WHERE E4.E4_userid=E2.E2_owneruserid)

CREATE VIEW E3 AS SELECT posthistory.userid AS E3_userid FROM posthistory AS posthistory WHERE CAST(posthistory.posthistorytypeid AS INTEGER) = 2 AND (posthistory.creationdate >= TIMESTAMP '2010-11-05 01:25:39' AND posthistory.creationdate <= TIMESTAMP '2014-09-09 07:14:12')
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E4_stage1_1 AS SELECT * FROM E4_stage1_0 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E3 WHERE E4_stage1_0.E4_userid=E3.E3_userid)
CREATE VIEW E5 AS SELECT users.id AS E5_id FROM users AS users WHERE users.views >= 0 AND users.views <= 13
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E4_stage1_2 AS SELECT * FROM E4_stage1_1 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E5 WHERE E4_stage1_1.E4_userid=E5.E5_id)
CREATE VIEW E1 AS SELECT comments.userid AS E1_userid FROM comments AS comments
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E4_stage1_3 AS SELECT * FROM E4_stage1_2 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E1 WHERE E4_stage1_2.E4_userid=E1.E1_userid)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E2_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E2 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E4_stage1_3 WHERE E4_stage1_3.E4_userid=E2.E2_owneruserid)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E3_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E3 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E4_stage1_3 WHERE E4_stage1_3.E4_userid=E3.E3_userid)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E5_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E5 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E4_stage1_3 WHERE E4_stage1_3.E4_userid=E5.E5_id)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E1_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E1 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E4_stage1_3 WHERE E4_stage1_3.E4_userid=E1.E1_userid)

CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E_stage3 AS SELECT E4_stage1_3.E4_userid AS E4_userid, E2_stage2_0.E2_owneruserid AS E2_owneruserid FROM E4_stage1_3, E2_stage2_0, E3_stage2_0, E5_stage2_0, E1_stage2_0 WHERE E4_stage1_3.E4_userid=E2_stage2_0.E2_owneruserid AND E4_stage1_3.E4_userid=E3_stage2_0.E3_userid AND E4_stage1_3.E4_userid=E5_stage2_0.E5_id AND E4_stage1_3.E4_userid=E1_stage2_0.E1_userid
